enormous black beam the sizre of the room grabbed the spark and pulled it 
into it absorbing it into his own power. The spark was now just apart of 
Galvatron with no way to escape or control anything it did anymore.
(the matrix of war has the power of 5 sparks so dont say it escaped cuz one 
spark cant match the power of 5. sorry.)
